{"type":"message","id":"9fc30011","parentId":"d9a21bd5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:03:26.400Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:cfd2966c-5e50-4153-ac26-a51b644dbe4a 每日AI科技早报] 请帮我搜索今日AI科技领域的热点新闻和重要资讯，整理成简洁清晰的早报内容发给用户。搜索关键词：AI、人工智能、大模型、OpenAI、ChatGPT、DeepSeek等。\n\n要求：\n1. 标题+简要说明\n2. 控制在5-10条以内\n3. 简洁清晰\n4. 早上9点发送，所以搜索的是最新动态\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 9:03 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 01:03 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775091806394}}
{"type":"message","id":"056b0916","parentId":"9fc30011","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:03:35.784Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务，需要我搜索今日AI科技热点新闻，整理成早报发给用户。当前时间是2026年4月2日早上9点03分。\n\n我需要：\n1. 搜索AI科技领域的最新新闻\n2. 整理成简洁清晰的早报\n3. 发送给用户\n\n让我先搜索相关新闻。","thinkingSignature":"dc6ad942db311ae7b8893a72d4deea807ef77775f9e45dbec32fb6ed69f02be6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3xxp7306gx62_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search && cat SKILL.md | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":117,"cacheRead":21187,"cacheWrite":23157,"totalTokens":44598,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00063561,"cacheWrite":0.00277884,"total":0.0035959499999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775091806397}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ce6271e","parentId":"056b0916","timestamp":"2026-04-02T01:03:35.800Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3xxp7306gx62_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775091815796}}
